            552.9359741210938,
            175.45199584960938
          ],
          "text": "RBI/2019-20/68 Master Direction DCM (CC) No.G-4/03.35.01/2019-20 July 01, 2019 (Updated as on October 03, 2019)",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b2",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.5,
            186.2400360107422,
            394.9598388671875,
            218.46005249023438
          ],
          "text": "1. The Chairman & Managing Director/Chief Executive Officer (All Banks having Currency Chests)",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b3",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.5,
            231.96006774902344,
            220.2012176513672,
            264.2400817871094
          ],
          "text": "2. The Director of Treasuries (State Governments)",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b4",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.5,
            277.152099609375,
            164.2559814453125,
            299.1720886230469
          ],
          "text": "Madam / Dear Sir",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b5",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.5,
            311.74810791015625,
            543.3386840820312,
            360.6720886230469
          ],
          "text": "Master Direction on Levy of Penal Interest for Delayed Reporting / Wrong Reporting / Non-Reporting of Currency Chest Transactions and Inclusion of Ineligible Amounts in Currency Chest Balances",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "Arial-BoldMT",
            "flags": 16,
            "is_bold": true,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b12",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            237.08990478515625,
            360.2225341796875,
            357.62628173828125,
            480.7589111328125
          ],
          "text": "Withdrawn",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 28.0,
            "name": "Arial",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b6",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.5,
            373.4400939941406,
            543.3387451171875,
            453.3000793457031
          ],
          "text": "In terms of the Preamble, under Section 45 of the RBI Act, 1934 and 35 A of the Banking Regulation Act, 1949, the Bank issues guidelines / instructions for realising the objectives of our Clean Note Policy. With a view to sustaining these efforts and ensure discipline among the banks on timely and accurate reporting of currency chest transactions, we have issued instructions on the subject.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b7",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.49998474121094,
            473.5199890136719,
            540.0182495117188,
            521.6400146484375
          ],
          "text": "2. The Master Direction enclosed incorporates updated guidelines / circulars on the subject. The Direction will be updated from time to time as and when fresh instructions are issued.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b8",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.5,
            541.2120361328125,
            468.5159912109375,
            563.2320556640625
          ],
          "text": "3. This Master Direction has been placed on RBI website at www.rbi.org.in.",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b9",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.5,
            589.260009765625,
            152.91600036621094,
            605.6400146484375
          ],
          "text": "Yours faithfully,",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b10",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.49998474121094,
            615.1799926757812,
            205.53599548339844,
            647.4000244140625
          ],
          "text": "(Manas Ranjan Mohanty) Chief General Manager",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        },
        {
          "block_id": "p1_b11",
          "type": "text",
          "bbox": [
            67.5,
            658.800048828125,
            154.23599243164062,
            675.1800537109375
          ],
          "text": "Encl : As above",
          "font_info": {
            "size": 12.0,
            "name": "ArialMT",
            "flags": 0,
            "is_bold": false,
            "is_italic": false
          }
        }
      ],
